                                
                                       I N S T A L L
   Requirements
  ------------
  The following requirements exist for running the PHP Toolkit:
   o  PHP Version 5.0.3 or higher
       
  Installation Instructions
  -------------------------
  Include  WebsmsCom_Toolkit.inc into your PHP File in order to access the classes and 
  methods for sending text and binary SMS.
  
  For PHP versions lower than 5.2.0 please make sure that JSON.phps is in the same directory as 
  WebsmsCom_Toolkit.inc or install Services_JSON from PEAR.
